description: This file defines modules and functions for handling browser list queries and configurations, primarily throwing errors for unsupported features in a client-side environment.

methods.name: loadQueries
methods.description: Throws an error indicating that sharable configs are not supported in client-side build.

methods.name: getStat
methods.description: Returns the 'stats' property from the provided options object.

methods.name: loadConfig
methods.description: Throws an error if a config is provided, indicating configs are not supported client-side.

methods.name: loadCountry
methods.description: Throws an error indicating country statistics are not supported in client-side build.

methods.name: loadFeature
methods.description: Throws an error indicating support queries are not available in client-side build.

methods.name: currentNode
methods.description: Returns the first value of the resolved array for maintained node versions.
